Class Human

java.lang.Object
com.example.projectfx.species.Species
com.example.projectfx.species.Omnivore
com.example.projectfx.species.Human
All Implemented Interfaces:
Movable, Reproducible, Sleepable
public class Human extends Omnivore
The Human class represents a human species in the ecosystem. This class extends the base Species class and adds unique human-specific behaviors such as movement, reproduction, defense mechanisms, and interaction with other species.
